HTML: Pushfor is a highly secure, content sharing and instant messaging appPushfor’s patented (US Patent No. 9660821) ‘push’ technology gives you total control when sharing and distributing content such as documents, presentations, photos, videos, images, music etc.  Pushfor is the perfect choice for sharing sensitive, confidential and high value content and for private chat conversations.  Content is ‘pushed’ not sent and can be pulled back at any time.Key features include:•    Original file never leaves source location so is highly secure•    Supports over 50 content types with no restrictions on file sizes•    No need for authoring software on recipient device•    High definition quality when viewing content•    Upload content from your device or any external cloud storage•    Share URL links and geo-location•    Push to individuals or groups – one push and content can be shared with many•    Tracking of every interaction so you know exactly who has viewed the content, where from, with what device and for how long•    Numerous viewing and privacy permissions •    Protection against screenshots•    Protection against Malware•    Watermarks can be applied•    Real-time engagement – messaging, text, voiceBe smart in how you share your content– Download now.At Pushfor we always like to hear about your feedback or suggestions on improvements. Get in touch at hello@pushfor.com
